To run this application, you will need the following:
Python 3.x
Flask 2.1.0
PyPDF2 1.26.0

Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/pdf-merger-web-app.git

Install the required packages:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Usage
Run the application:
python pdf_merger_app.py
Open your web browser and go to http://localhost:5000/.
Select multiple PDF files to upload and merge.
Click on the "Merge" button to merge the uploaded PDF files.
The merged PDF file will be downloaded automatically.
